    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a genus containing over 1,000 species of ant large ants that create nests in dead, damp wood or hollow out sections of trees. They may infest buildings made of wood. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
